sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Dev as Developer
    participant ADO as Azure DevOps
    participant VS as VS Code
    participant Git as Local Git Repo
    participant App as Local App / Test Runner

    Dev->>ADO: Open project → Repos → Branches
    Dev->>ADO: Create new branch from main\nExample: feature/event-search
    Dev->>ADO: Copy repository clone URL
    Dev->>VS: Open VS Code

    alt Repo not cloned locally
        Dev->>Git: git clone https://dev.azure.com/org/project/_git/repo
        Dev->>Git: cd repo
        Dev->>VS: code .
    else Repo already cloned locally
        Dev->>Git: cd repo
        Dev->>VS: code .
    end

    Dev->>Git: git fetch origin
    Dev->>Git: git checkout feature/event-search

    alt Local branch does not exist
        Dev->>Git: git checkout -b feature/event-search --track origin/feature/event-search
    else Local branch already exists
        Note over Dev,Git: Use existing local feature branch
    end

    loop Development cycle until work complete
        Dev->>VS: Edit files in VS Code
        Dev->>Git: git status
        Dev->>App: npm install
        Dev->>App: npm run dev
        Dev->>App: npm test
    end

    Dev->>Git: git add .
    Dev->>Git: git commit -m "Implement event search improvements"
    Dev->>Git: git push origin feature/event-search
    Git->>ADO: Push feature branch

    alt Main has changed
        Dev->>Git: git fetch origin
        Dev->>Git: git checkout feature/event-search
        Dev->>Git: git rebase origin/main

        alt Rebase conflicts occur
            loop Resolve until no conflicts remain
                Dev->>VS: Resolve conflicts
                Dev->>Git: git status
                Dev->>Git: git add .
                Dev->>Git: git rebase --continue
            end
        else No rebase conflicts
            Note over Dev,Git: Rebase completes cleanly
        end

        Dev->>App: npm test
        Dev->>Git: git push --force-with-lease origin feature/event-search
        Git->>ADO: Update rebased branch
    else Main has not changed
        Note over Dev,ADO: No rebase needed
    end

    alt Not ready to create PR
        Dev->>Git: git status
        Note over Dev,Git: Continue development on same branch
    else Ready to create PR
        Dev->>ADO: Create Pull Request\nSource: feature/event-search\nTarget: main
        ADO->>ADO: Run reviewers, policies, validation, build checks

        alt PR not approved or checks fail
            loop Address feedback until approved
                Dev->>VS: Edit files to address feedback
                Dev->>Git: git add .
                Dev->>Git: git commit -m "Address PR feedback"
                Dev->>Git: git push origin feature/event-search
                Git->>ADO: Update PR branch
                ADO->>ADO: Re-run review and checks
            end
        else PR approved and checks passed
            Dev->>ADO: Complete / merge Pull Request into main
            opt Optionally delete remote branch
                Dev->>ADO: Delete remote branch
            end
            Dev->>Git: git checkout main
            Dev->>Git: git pull origin main

            alt More work to do
                Dev->>Git: git checkout -b feature/next-task
                Note over Dev,Git: Start next development cycle
            else No more work
                Note over Dev,ADO: End workflow
            end
        end
    end